Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm Kenta Ochiai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distracted by thoughts of girls in bikinis,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got tricked into a part-time job at a resort hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt looks like it might collapse at any minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's run by some old loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To top it off, l can't even pick up girls, because Suwatee and Shuree came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was attacked by the Amazon Gang and got beat up by a gangster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt sucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then l met the adorable Mahoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can feel waves of love in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't let them become tidal waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone, come and get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who's hip eats hamburgers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, two strawberry and three melon snow cones, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that kid is the rich old man's grandkid? Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Typical Kenta, drooling all over her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:01:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Namiya, come to my office immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! You really helped out today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's been a long time since l had this much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls it okay if l come help tomorrow too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! l'd love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Kenta, see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Mahoko. She's such a nice girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sweet and cute too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need a cold shower, so you can think about how much you just hurt Suwatee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An enormous typhoon is steadily growing stronger...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and is headed toward Hokuoku lsland at 20km per hour.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that typhoon headed for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. lt'll be here in four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should get ready for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, watch your step...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Mr. Sanada?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sanada, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Seiichi Sanada - Champion, All Japan Surf Competition''.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sanada, were you a surfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, l was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:04:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought it was a great way to pick up girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cool! You shouldn't be embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why can't l help Kenta and his friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l put everything l have into this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l also invested considerable money on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanada is the only one who stands in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helping them and their hotel is betraying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so narrow-minded!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not a kid anymore! l can do what l want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, she's at a difficult age.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt may not be wise to try and control her too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet. This is between my granddaughter and l.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suwatee, cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're having a Summer Festival at the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she's not going, so leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, why don't you and l go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tricked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ldiot! Now she's really mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! How do l look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l asked you how l looked!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think l look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're beautiful! Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Shuree took the best and cutest yukata!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the one l wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing, l didn't know that was the one she had her eye on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't wear the same one as Shuree!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suwatee, can l come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was cleaning out a box, and l found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think it'll look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can l really have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's just gathering dust. You take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clumsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to buy one for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want from me in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, it's just to be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding! Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l'd love one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick out the one you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to get the cheapest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wouldn't have minded spending more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not that. l just liked this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you can be so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really. Spare me the sweet talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l still deny anything happening between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting upset about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blow it this time, lover boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suwatee...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can l buy you some takoyaki? Or maybe some cotton candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'd like a snow cone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're such a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old guy was the All-Japan Surfing Champion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought he was just some loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was surprised, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Those two are getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All it needs to be perfect is a little music.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, how about we help them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm hoping you've finally cheered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you think of me as a little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's okay to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know l'm childish sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but l'm ready to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush things, Suwatee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all overwhelmed by our feelings sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but basically life is pretty simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're unsure,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can always find the truth in your own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now how about we get it on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You totally ruined the mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sure no Prince Charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hear you're chasing little Miss Mahoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l knew you were dumb,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's really stupid even for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was really upset about her grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really pissed that Mahoko is working at your hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got into a huge fight over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, he's really protective of Mahoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shuree? Are you still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Kenta and l aren't meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always got some other girl and doesn't even notice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the gods are telling me to just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Little Miss l-Used-To-Be-A-Goddess, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't really believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you'll just give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget him just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf not, you'll just have to try harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, why is it so important for you to get us together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, you aren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the last time, l am not interested!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:14:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not my type at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go to sleep! Good night, Suwatee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Shuree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another long day at work...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope not. You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with them? Those guys are all over her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come out with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're free tonight. Pick us up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Score! Yeah, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make Kenta jealous by going out with another guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick us up here at seven, okay? Don't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:14:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Pick us up here at seven, okay? Don't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:14:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suwatee, what do you think of this outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit worrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:16:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now he's so worried about you, that he can't think straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys ready for the next outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This isn't a fashion show!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going dancing with Shuree, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, l really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Suwatee, hurry up! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, hurry up! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee! Suwatee, hurry up! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, hurry up! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Suwatee, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:17:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, how could you transfer me to a different school without even asking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seika Girls Academy is very strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's perfect for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l won't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girls school... l'd rather be here, at the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, that was too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What have l done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's them. lt's their fault that Mahoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll make them pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hate eating dinner all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, your grandfather really did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l understand his feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents died when l was four.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm the only family he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not that l'm not interested in our hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just don't think we have to destroy everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt'll be okay! Just try talking to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he treats me like a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no helping that... you are still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Kenta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not a child anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l... lt's my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! lt feels strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't stare at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's beautiful, Mahoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be gentle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahoko, you're so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, l'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a drag!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.47,0:23:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing as depressing as a woman in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about Kenta, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll stay here with the guys. Go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.61,0:23:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.79,0:23:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't argue with a woman in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.16,0:24:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mina...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.91,0:24:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.02,0:24:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.26,0:25:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up! l'll help you talk to your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.01,0:25:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.90,0:25:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.47,0:25:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's your grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.67,0:25:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.98,0:25:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.12,0:25:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.16,0:26:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one interfering with my Mahoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.28,0:26:33.41,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sagashi tsuzuketeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.28,0:26:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have the one bright smile...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.99,0:26:40.92,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kagayaku sono egao{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.99,0:26:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that l've always been looking for.{\i0}
