Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.01,0:28:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT TlME
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.05,0:28:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta's a jerk, doing it with that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.99,0:28:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now there's a surfing contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.12,0:28:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Suwatee?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.36,0:28:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm tired of waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.16,0:28:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm going to risk everything! l'm going to take a stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.03,0:28:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l won't let anyone else win Kenta's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.04,0:28:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Can Can Bunny Extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.01,0:28:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Suwatee. Goodbye, Kenta.
